r />\n點樣確保Object key嘅次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咗個小實驗:<br />\n以英文嚟講, 無論Array.sort(), Array.reverse(), 同localeCompare()都好正常;<br />\n但一轉做中文, 就怪怪的:<br />\n- 個sorting同reverse sorting正好同英文調L轉,<br />\n  i.e. d &gt; c &gt; b &gt; a (in English), but 甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 (in Chinese), 唔知點解?! <br />\n<br />\n- 個香港locale(i.e. zh-Hans-HK)就睇嚟係以粵語拼音嚟排, 但用咗邊隻粵拼版本就唔知了!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgh.us/ObjectKeySorting.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgh.us%2FObjectKeySorting.jpg&h=2b833dfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12e1b223039384b29f011f889fe859946856b89e","tid":316922,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n...<br />\n點樣確保Object key嘅次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咗個小實驗:<br />\n以英文嚟講, 無論Array.sort(), Array.reverse(), 同localeCompare()都好正常;<br />\n但一轉做中文, 就怪怪的:<br />\n- 個sorting同reverse sorting正好同英文調L轉,<br />\n  i.e. d &gt; c &gt; b &gt; a (in English), but 甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 (in Chinese), 唔知點解?! <br />\n<br />\n- 個香港locale(i.e. zh-Hans-HK)就睇嚟係以粵語拼音嚟排, 但用咗邊隻粵拼版本就唔知了!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgh.us/ObjectKeySorting.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgh.us%2FObjectKeySorting.jpg&h=2b833dfb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺咗啲code係pastebin度, 方便大家download落嚟試:<br />\n<a href=\"https://pastebin.com/TrW3jEig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FTrW3jEig&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=30c89aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/TrW3jEig</a>"},{"pid":"27be701caead96cefeaa442f4239004fdf92ec9f","tid":316922,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n...<br />\n點樣確保Object key嘅次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咗個小實驗:<br />\n以英文嚟講, 無論Array.sort(), Array.reverse(), 同localeCompare()都好正常;<br />\n但一轉做中文, 就怪怪的:<br />\n- 個sorting同reverse sorting正好同英文調L轉,<br />\n  i.e. d &gt; c &gt; b &gt; a (in English), but 甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 (in Chinese), 唔知點解?! <br />\n<br />\n- 個香港locale(i.e. zh-Hans-HK)就睇嚟係以粵語拼音嚟排, 但用咗邊隻粵拼版本就唔知了!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgh.us/ObjectKeySorting.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgh.us%2FObjectKeySorting.jpg&h=2b833dfb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺咗啲code係pastebin度, 方便大家download落嚟試:<br />\n<a href=\"https://pastebin.com/TrW3jEig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FTrW3jEig&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=30c89aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/TrW3jEig</a></blockquote><br />\n但係你&quot;藍超係On9仔&quot;嗰個冇做Sorting<br />\n係咪-6"},{"pid":"f410928bce267b1d1b38f43b5ff4486db52a40fe","tid":316922,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n...<br />\n點樣確保Object key嘅次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咗個小實驗:<br />\n以英文嚟講, 無論Array.sort(), Array.reverse(), 同localeCompare()都好正常;<br />\n但一轉做中文, 就怪怪的:<br />\n- 個sorting同reverse sorting正好同英文調L轉,<br />\n  i.e. d &gt; c &gt; b &gt; a (in English), but 甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 (in Chinese), 唔知點解?! <br />\n<br />\n- 個香港locale(i.e. zh-Hans-HK)就睇嚟係以粵語拼音嚟排, 但用咗邊隻粵拼版本就唔知了!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgh.us/ObjectKeySorting.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgh.us%2FObjectKeySorting.jpg&h=2b833dfb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺咗啲code係pastebin度, 方便大家download落嚟試:<br />\n<a href=\"https://pastebin.com/TrW3jEig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FTrW3jEig&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=30c89aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/TrW3jEig</a></blockquote><br />\n但係你&quot;藍超係On9仔&quot;嗰個冇做Sorting<br />\n係咪-6</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一, sort黎做乜先?! Pop出黎做到野咪得囉。<br />\n第二, 如果要sort, 都唔知用乜基準, 粵拼定注音定筆畫先?<br />\n第三, 呢個仲要中英夾雜, 點為之sort得啱呢?<br />\n<br />\n總之, 要sorting就咪鬼用中文做key, 盞玩死自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3515a41230c71ebc8ff718e5852956b16418b167","tid":316922,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n...<br />\n點樣確保Object key嘅次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咗個小實驗:<br />\n以英文嚟講, 無論Array.sort(), Array.reverse(), 同localeCompare()都好正常;<br />\n但一轉做中文, 就怪怪的:<br />\n- 個sorting同reverse sorting正好同英文調L轉,<br />\n  i.e. d &gt; c &gt; b &gt; a (in English), but 甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 (in Chinese), 唔知點解?! <br />\n<br />\n- 個香港locale(i.e. zh-Hans-HK)就睇嚟係以粵語拼音嚟排, 但用咗邊隻粵拼版本就唔知了!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgh.us/ObjectKeySorting.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgh.us%2FObjectKeySorting.jpg&h=2b833dfb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 就梗係unicode啦"},{"pid":"332986bd41d5d16dab04ebd462cff7911cb7d462","tid":316922,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"&gt;&gt;&gt; [ord(char) for char in '甲乙丙丁戊己庚申壬癸']<br />\n[30002, 20057, 19993, 19969, 25098, 24049, 24218, 30003, 22764, 30328]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07d5cc7650c310d7cf26c8b2db1f13f90667052","tid":316922,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n...<br />\n點樣確保Object key嘅次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咗個小實驗:<br />\n以英文嚟講, 無論Array.sort(), Array.reverse(), 同localeCompare()都好正常;<br />\n但一轉做中文, 就怪怪的:<br />\n- 個sorting同reverse sorting正好同英文調L轉,<br />\n  i.e. d &gt; c &gt; b &gt; a (in English), but 甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 (in Chinese), 唔知點解?! <br />\n<br />\n- 個香港locale(i.e. zh-Hans-HK)就睇嚟係以粵語拼音嚟排, 但用咗邊隻粵拼版本就唔知了!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgh.us/ObjectKeySorting.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgh.us%2FObjectKeySorting.jpg&h=2b833dfb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n甲 &gt; 乙 &gt; 丙 &gt; 丁 就梗係unicode啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎, 唔該晒! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過咁就PK喇, 因為跟unicode排, 咁原本以為可以:<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">甲、乙、丙、丁、戊、己、庚、辛、壬、癸</span>咁用Array.reverse()順排, 點知結果係:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">辛、癸、甲、 戊、 庚、己、 壬、 乙、 丙、 丁</span>咁L樣排法, 唉!<br />\n<br />\n一二三四五六七八九十呢? <br />\n用Array.sort()就排成一七三九二五八六十四<br />\n用Array.reverse()就排成四十六八五二九三七一 <br />\n<br />\n總之都係唔掂當! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(Conclusion: Never use Chinese as object keys! Never!)"},{"pid":"25eb59c0dcd359411757a64bbf687663c672f6d4","tid":316922,"uid":24795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"MCHK巴一嚟就pop舊野<br />\n咁咪由下到上囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}